::: {.question-block}

<form onsubmit="event.preventDefault();" style="display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;"> <label for="module9_num_q4b_single"><strong>b. $PV(\text{distress})$ (millions):</strong></label> <input type="number" id="module9_num_q4b_single" name="module9_num_q4b_single" style="width:160px;" data-correct-answer=22.7 data-tolerance="1" step="0.01" /> </form> <div id="feedback-module9_num_q4b_single" class="feedback" data-status="" style="display:none;"> ‚úÖ $PV(\text{distress}) = p \times L = 0.28 \times 81.08 =$ <b>22.7M</b>. </div>
