::: {.question-block}

<form onsubmit="event.preventDefault();" style="display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;"> <label for="module9_num_q4d_single"><strong>d. Net effect of leverage $V_L - V_U$ (millions):</strong></label> <input type="number" id="module9_num_q4d_single" name="module9_num_q4d_single" style="width:160px;" data-correct-answer=2.13 data-tolerance="1" step="0.01" /> </form> <div id="feedback-module9_num_q4d_single" class="feedback" data-status="" style="display:none;"> ‚úÖ $V_L - V_U = PV(\text{tax shield}) - PV(\text{distress}) = 24.83 - 22.7 =$ <b>2.13M</b>. </div>
